Executive Summary 3



Troubles that occurred during the project:

1. JSON File had a complex object name that makes the JSON file to produce error in the script task. I resolve it by taking out the column manually from each file since it is a result of longitude and latitude(redundant).

2. After loading the JSON File to the staging table in the staging Database, I find out that Year 2018 data didn't load from the source.  I reloaded the data from the source and run the package again to solve the problem.

3. The source CSV has over 6 million records and to convert it to JSON, I have to split it to 100K files and run it on CSV to JSON convertor 70 times. so I decided to use only a few years of data (2017 -2020) since trying to run the whole data was taking hrs.
